      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent review of simulation setup by a second analyst; documented checklist for boundary condition assignment and material property selection.",
      "rationale": "No independent second-analyst review was performed. Single-analyst setup without documented checklist. Epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1."
